{
 "_readme": [
  "Jurisdiction registry for the generic open-data connectors (Socrata, ArcGIS).",
  "COVERAGE GROWS BY APPENDING ENTRIES, NEVER BY WRITING CONNECTOR CODE. There is no",
  "jurisdiction-specific logic anywhere in sources/socrata.ts or sources/arcgis.ts \u2014 a new",
  "city is one more object in this file. See docs/source-registry.md.",
  "",
  "RULES (enforced by the connector + the run report):",
  "  \u2022 status_to_bucket values are copied VERBATIM from the dataset's live distinct status",
  "    values (query SELECT DISTINCT via SoQL first \u2014 never guessed). A status not listed in",
  "    any bucket is logged in the run report, the record is EXCLUDED, and it never lands in a band.",
  "  \u2022 coverage is state + county (or state alone for a statewide dataset). The engine filters",
  "    to the ZIPs HomeSignal actually serves, so adding a ZIP never touches this file.",
  "  \u2022 type_map maps a VERBATIM source classification value to one of the six use-types:",
  "    Industrial | Development | Residential | Utility | Commercial | Civic/Public.",
  "    An unmapped/absent value \u2192 use_type:'unclassified' (logged), never inferred from the title.",
  "  \u2022 record_url: from the column named in column_map.record_url when present (string, or an",
  "    object whose .url is used), else record_url_template with {case_number}/{<col>} filled,",
  "    else the dataset landing page with record_url_precision:'dataset'."
 ],
 "_arcgis_readme": [
  "ArcGIS FeatureServer connector (sources/arcgis.ts) \u2014 the Esri twin of the Socrata one.",
  "Same discipline: append an entry here, never edit the connector. An entry needs:",
  "  registry_id, platform:'arcgis', service_url (the LAYER query base .../FeatureServer/0),",
  "  dataset_url (record_url fallback), jurisdiction, coverage[{state,county}],",
  "  column_map (read point lat/lng from geometry via the flattened '__lat'/'__lng' columns),",
  "  status_to_bucket (VERBATIM live distinct values \u2014 query first, never guess),",
  "  type_map (verbatim class -> Industrial|Development|Residential|Utility|Commercial|Civic/Public),",
  "  optional: record_url_template, recency_days, max_rows, out_sr (default 4326).",
  "The ZIP column is MANDATORY. STATUS: connector BUILT + unit-tested + wired (arcgisForZip).",
  "Add verified entries here as clean per-address permit/case FeatureServers are confirmed."
 ],
